{"id":232867140,"title":"薪水真的可以抵平一切嗎？","content":"https://youtu.be/EeoiOonpRVQ\n上面這則舊新聞有提到一些護理的辛酸重點，也指出了護病比這個一直沒有得到解決的問題\n\n其實早就想問這個問題很久了，各位護理界的可愛護理師們，想請問如果職場讓你們覺得血汗，受盡委屈，壓榨，面對病患，面對醫師，面對學姊刁難等等情事，真的只要提高薪資就可以讓你們覺得沒關係嗎？\n我個人覺得再高都沒有用，相信離職率高也不是薪資可以解決的，想聽聽看各位的想法\n\n最後想說的是台灣醫療業環境已經沒有很友善了，大家今天可以投票的請一定要去投票，因如果讓健保開放這件事成真，相信苦的是你我每一個人，醫療人員的負擔一定再更加重，這絕對是我們都不樂見的事","excerpt":"上面這則舊新聞有提到一些護理的辛酸重點，也指出了護病比這個一直沒有得到解決的問題，其實早就想問這個問題很久了，各位護理界的可愛護理師們，想請問如果職場讓你們覺得血汗，受盡委屈，壓榨，面對病患，面對醫師","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"b22d2f5d-3c06-4d08-96b8-770eb38e8f96","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-10T17:14:34.541Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-10T17:14:34.541Z","commentCount":17,"likeCount":59,"tags":[],"topics":["薪水","護理師","工作","心情","壓力"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"護理","forumAlias":"nursing","school":"台南應用科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":59}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"194ce897-b2a3-4401-bfaa-70f0de394347","url":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/EeoiOonpRVQ/hqdefault.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/EeoiOonpRVQ/hqdefault.jpg","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/EeoiOonpRVQ/hqdefault.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-10T17:14:34.541Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-10T17:14:34.541Z"},{"id":"194ce897-b2a3-4401-bfaa-70f0de394347","url":"https://youtu.be/EeoiOonpRVQ","normalizedUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EeoiOonpRVQ","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/EeoiOonpRVQ/hqdefault.jpg","type":"video/youtube","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-10T17:14:34.541Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-10T17:14:34.541Z"}],"postAvatar":""}